observations.recommendation:
4.7	We recommended that:
The Municipal Accountant –
Prepares the necessary adjusting entries for the Due to BIR account;
Withheld from each employee the amount of tax deficiency covering the CY 2024 supplementary compensation, and henceforward, avoid the same miscalculation;
The Municipal Treasurer remits the tax deficiencies noted on compensation income for CY 2024.
4.8	The concerned officials agreed to comply with the audit recommendations.

We recommended that:

The Municipal Accountant– 

Record adjustments for the accounting errors noted, after verification and supported with documents;

Refrain from drawing unsupported entries in the journals and ledgers, and henceforth, ensure that all journal entries and ledger postings have supporting documents attached;

Assign a staff who would be in charge of securing copies of the bank statements/snapshots and other related documents, to facilitate the prompt preparation of the monthly BRS; and

Prepare the CY 2023 BRS for each bank account maintained by the Municipality, duly supported with documents, and submit the same to COA for verification. Henceforth, strictly observe its monthly preparation and submission to COA.
